name: Research paper on V2V Communication
desc: The rapid modernization of technology in recent decades has brought significant advancements and upgrades across various industries, including automotive. The integration of AI/ML, IoT, and digitalization has revolutionized the automotive industry, enhancing efficiency, security, and connectivity. Additionally, the establishment of vehicle-to-vehicle communication networks holds great potential for improving transportation management, productivity, and future readiness for autonomous vehicles.
